title: Get suburb details based on cityName, and suburbName.
description: Get suburb details based on cityName, and suburbName. Accepted combinations should be city name, followed with the suburb name. All space should be replaced with dash. E.g "new-plymouth/highlands-park"

returns.description: <SoldSuburbSearchResponse> Details of the suburb, and its surrounding suburbs.

fields.name: PropertiesRecentlySold
fields.description: To list down Properties that are recently sold in the suburb Filtered by ‘ForSale' = true, DateMax = today’s date, DateMin = start of last month; to get the number of houses for sale in the past month.
